\[Sigma]\)]\) are differentiation wrt proper time \[Tau] and \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[StyleBox[\"A\",FontSize->12], StyleBox[FormBox[StyleBox[\
\"\[Prime]\",FontSize->14,FontWeight->\"Regular\",FontSlant->\"Plain\"],\
